,{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"私もこの曲を歌いたい。\nこんな風に心揺さぶる音楽を……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"memorial106-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"……この曲を歌う、父のように。\nそう、思ったのだけど……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"memorial106-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"私にこの歌が歌えるかどうか、不安だったの。\nこの曲に求められるスキルは相当高いものが必要よ。\n……でも、それだけじゃない","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"memorial106-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"私に……この歌を歌う資格があるのか。\nそれがわからなかった","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":21,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":21,"voiceId":"memorial106-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":21}],"windowDisplayName":"友希那","body":"この曲から感じられる純粋で、ひたむきな音楽への情熱……\nそれを、私が歌っていいの？","tention":0,"